  "text": "In view of the discussion above, (i) immediately implies that E is a flat O-module. The proof of Theorem 1.1 relies on of the construction of weighted integral representation formulas in [CITATION_1] , the residue currents associated with free resolutions in [CITATION_2] Section 5] , and the special choice of weight in [CITATION_3] .",
